_json.description: Nothing finishes off a seating area like throw pillows. Layered or on their own, a good throw pillow can add colour, comfort and consistency. Over the years, I’ve discovered some simple guidelines to styling pillows on sofas, benches and chairs and I’m sharing them on the blog today. Click the link in my bio.
